data.description: Awesome two story home only 3 miles from the new Buc-ee's with open concept, bonus room, beautiful flat fenced backyard, Private Inground POOL as well as a huge 2.12 Acres that could possibly be subdivided into two additional lots!! All stainless-steel kitchen appliances, washer / dryer and pool furniture will convey! This house is a newer 2019 built house but the owner added new cabinets in the laundry room and the Pool and New Fence about a year ago including new fresh stain on the fence last week! Additional features include: Large open concept on main level with large kitchen, kitchen island, pantry, walk out to pool, fireplace, Large Master bedroom with huge walk in closet, large master bath, walk in shower, dual vanities and a water closet! Also a bonus room that could make a great office space or kids play area and a two car garage! When you step outside, enjoy the privacy fence that surrounds your own private pool and grilling area. Also enjoy a total of 2.12 Acres that you could use in a lot of different ways. Seller has already considered building a mother-in-law suite as well as subdividing the land to build on! Enjoy all of this with NO HOA, County only taxes, and easy access to grocery, restaurants, Buc-ee's, interstate 40 and pigeon forge. With all the new developments coming to this area, don't pass up checking out this awesome house!!
